  "format": "lake",
  "body": "`rpx（responsive pixel）`: 可以根据屏幕宽度进行自适应。规定屏幕宽为 `750rpx`。公式：\n```javascript\nconst dsWidth = 750\n\nexport const screenHeightOfRpx = function () {\n  return 750 / env.screenWidth * env.screenHeight\n}\n\nexport const rpxToPx = function (rpx) {\n  return env.screenWidth / 750 * rpx\n}\n\nexport const pxToRpx = function (px) {\n  return 750 / env.screenWidth * px\n}\n```\n",
  "body_draft": "",
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u50cefad0\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">rpx（responsive pixel）</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 可以根据屏幕宽度进行自适应。规定屏幕宽为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">750rpx</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。公式：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"kLVLP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\">const dsWidth = 750\n\nexport const screenHeightOfRpx = function () {\n  return 750 / env.screenWidth * env.screenHeight\n}\n\nexport const rpxToPx = function (rpx) {\n  return env.screenWidth / 750 * rpx\n}\n\nexport const pxToRpx = function (px) {\n  return 750 / env.screenWidth * px\n}</pre></div>",
